ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Infrastructure, Communities and Intergovernmental Affairs of MARIE ANTOINETTE CAMPAGNA of LaSalle, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of the Windsor-Detroit Bridge Authority to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until a successor is appointed, whichever occurs first.
